  • Bluetooth Call & Smart Notification: Smart watches for men women is equipped with a built-in microphone and HD speaker, which allows you to make and receive calls when connected to your smartphone via Bluetooth. The smartwatch can remind you with a ringtone or vibration, and receive notifications from apps such as Facebook, Whatsapp, Instagram, SMS, etc. You can stay connected at any time, even during fitness or other activities
  • 24/7 Health Monitoring: Fitness watch is equipped with high-precision sensors, 24-hour real-time heart rate, Sp02, and sleep monitoring (deep/light sleep/awake), you can also view these health indicators on the smart watch anytime, anywhere, and view the recent data in the APP so that you can better understand your physical health. In addition, women's smart watch also has a menstrual cycle record designed specifically for women to help them maintain a healthy life
  • 100+ Sports Modes & IP68 Waterproof: The activity fitness tracker has 100+ sports modes to choose from, including running, cycling, hiking, skipping, basketball, yoga, skiing, etc. It can record all-day exercise data and accurately track your exercise time, calories burned, distance, and steps. It meets the IP68 waterproof rating and can be used without worry even when washing hands, washing face, or engaging in sweaty activities, but it is not recommended to use it in hot water or seawater
  • 1.85 inch HD Color Screen & DIY Watch Face: Smart watch is equipped with a 1.85" HD full touch screen, delivering highly sensitive touch and unique visual feast. With the companion GloryFit App, you can download more than 200+ personalized watch faces and set them as your dial. In addition, you can also choose your favorite photos, such as family, personal photos, pets, landscapes, etc. as the wallpaper of your watch
  • Multifunctional Smartwatch & Wide Compatibility: The smart watch includes many useful tools, such as Bluetooth answering/making calls, message reminders, female health cycle, weather forecast, music control/playback, camera control, alarm clock, stopwatch, timer, breathing guide, sedentary reminder, raise to wake, brightness adjustment, find phone and other functions. Joautrial smart watch is compatible with iOS 9.0 and Android 6.0 and above devices
  • Satisfy Every Customer: We are committed to providing you with great purchasing. If you have any questions about our products, such as missing watch accessories, or quality/operation connection/charging issues, please let us know and contact us to resolve. Warm Tips: Please wear your smartwatch correctly, the strap should not be tied too tight or too loose, and leave space for your skin to breathe, which will not only make you feel comfortable but also allow the smart watch sensor to work properly

      Its easy to use, looks great
      Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2024
      1.
      From the stylish design to its amazing features, this smartwatch has exceeded my expectations in so many ways. It has really become an essential part of my routine. The color is really pretty, and it goes with almost everything I wear. Whether Im wearing casual clothes or... See more
      From the stylish design to its amazing features, this smartwatch has exceeded my expectations in so many ways. It has really become an essential part of my routine. The color is really pretty, and it goes with almost everything I wear. Whether Im wearing casual clothes or something a bit more dressy, this watch fits perfectly. The watch face is sleek and modern, and its not too bulky, so its super comfortable on my wrist. Plus, the screen is bright and clear, which makes it easy to read even in sunlight. Ive worn it for long hours, and I barely even notice its there.
      One of my favorite things about this smartwatch is the battery life. It lasts for several days without needing a charge, which is super convenient. And when I do need to charge it, it charges really fast. This feature has made it so much easier to use daily because Im not constantly thinking about charging it.
      The health tracking features are another reason Im so happy with this watch. It helps me keep track of my daily activity, like my step count, and sends me reminders to move if Ive been sitting for too long. This has really helped me stay active. The heart rate monitor is also awesome it gives me real-time data on how my heart is doing, which is great for both workouts and just everyday life. I especially love the sleep monitor, which tracks how well Im sleeping. This smartwatch has over 100 sport modes! I didnt expect it to have so many options, but its great for any kind of exercise Im doing. Whether Im running, biking, doing yoga, or even swimming, theres a mode that tracks everything I need. Its really motivating to see my progress in different activities.
      The smartwatch also helps me stay connected. I can get notifications for messages, emails, and social media alerts right on my wrist, which is super convenient. I dont always have to pull my phone out of my bag or pocket to check updates, and I can respond to messages directly from the watch.       This smartwatch delivers a surprisingly robust feature set for its price point. Its ability to make and receive Bluetooth calls, paired with message notifications, is highly convenient. I found the interface straightforward to navigate, and syncing the watch with my phone took no more than a few minutes. The notifications are customizable, allowing me to choose which apps I get alerts from, which helps minimize distractions throughout the day.

      The 1.39 HD screen is larger than I expected, and the resolution is crisp, making it easy to read texts, even in direct sunlight. I was particularly impressed with the selection of dial wallpapers. You can even upload your own images, which adds a personal touch. The screens touch responsiveness is smooth, and switching between modes feels intuitive.

      Health tracking features are where this watch really shines. It includes everything from heart rate and blood oxygen monitoring to sleep tracking and a pedometer. The accuracy of the heart rate monitor held up well when compared to other fitness trackers Ive used, and the sleep tracker provided detailed insights that have helped me improve my nightly routine. Additionally, it supports over 100 sports modes, which is far more than I could ever need, but its a nice bonus for anyone who wants that level of fitness tracking.

      Charging is quick and efficient, with a full charge lasting me around 3 days on moderate use. Given the price, the battery life is solid, and the fact that its so easy to recharge means it never felt like a hassle to keep up with. If youre looking for an affordable smartwatch with a broad range of features, this is a reliable choice.
